longBusinessSummary: DSG Global Inc., a technology development company, engages in the design, manufacture, and marketing of fleet management solutions for the golf industry, commercial, government, and military applications worldwide. It develops, sells, and rents GPS tracking devices and interfaces for the golf industry, as well as provides related support services. The company also offers golfer information display systems and golf carts. In addition, it imports, markets, and distributes a range of low-speed and high-speed electric passenger vehicles for commuter, family, commercial, and public use. The company is based in Surrey, Canada.
